%C A208855 All primitive Pythagorean triples are given by
%C A208855 (a(n,m)=A208854(n,m),b(n,m),c(n,m)= A208853(n,m)), n>=1, m>=1. If the entry is 0 there is no primitive Pythagorean triple for these n and m values.
